Yiqi Ni, Founder & CEO
Yiqi Ni, Founder & CEO Yiqi is the founder and CEO of Accretion LLC. Yiqi created Accretion after graduation in 2023 from MIT with a Ph.D. degree in physics. With a passion for experimentation, statistics and physics models, Yiqi created Accretion to lower barrier of entry to the housing market.
